520
01:19:17,257 --> 01:19:20,052
¿Que tal si nos dices algo, Lowell?

521
01:19:24,640 --> 01:19:26,266
Hola.

522
01:19:26,391 --> 01:19:28,227
¿Lowell?

523
01:19:28,393 --> 01:19:30,854
Me alegro de verte, chico.

524
01:19:32,773 --> 01:19:35,526
- ¿Quién es?
